high_descs: Turn around and face the sink on the left.
Pick the sponge on the right up from the sink.
Turn around and face the trash can in the corner.
Put the sponge in the trash can.
Turn around and cross the room to face the sink on the left.
Pick the sponge up from the sink.
Cross the room and face the trash can on the floor.
Put the sponge in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put two sponges in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink and then take a half step to your right.
Pick up the sponge on the right side of the sink to the right of the other sponge.
TUrn around and walk to the door then turn right and walk to the garbage.
Put the sponge in the garbage.
Go back to where you got the first sponge.
Pick up the sponge.
Go back to where you put the first sponge.
Put this sponge in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Put two sponges in the garbage.

high_descs: Go to the left sink behind you.
Pick up the sponge on the right.
Turn to your left to face the corner wastebasket and go to it.
Drop the sponge into the wastebasket.
Turn right and return to the sink.
Pick up the remaining sponge from the sink.
Return to the wastebasket.
Throw the sponge in the wastebasket.
anns.task_desc: Discard two sponges in a bathroom wastebasket.
